Package: book-scraper-api
Version: 1.0-1
Section: web
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: python3, python3-venv, ufw, systemd
Maintainer: AMA <ama@example.com>
Description: A web scraper and FastAPI service for fetching book data.
 This package sets up a FastAPI network service that pulls data from books.toscrape.com
 and serves it over port 8888. It includes an automatic systemd setup and ufw firewall rules.
